{"number":80,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","translation":"He [i.e., the Prophet (ﷺ) ] frowned and turned away","transliteration":"AAabasa watawalla","page":585},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلْأَعْمَىٰ","translation":"Because there came to him the blind man, [interrupting].","transliteration":"An jaahu al-aAAma","page":585},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","translation":"But what would make you perceive, [O Muḥammad], that perhaps he might be purified","transliteration":"Wama yudreeka laAAallahu yazzakka","page":585},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰٓ","translation":"Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him?","transliteration":"Aw yaththakkaru fatanfaAAahu aththikra","page":585},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسْتَغْنَىٰ","translation":"As for he who thinks himself without need,","transliteration":"Amma mani istaghna","page":585},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","translation":"To him you give attention.","transliteration":"Faanta lahu tasadda","page":585},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","translation":"And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified.","transliteration":"Wama AAalayka alla yazzakka","page":585},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ","translation":"But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]","transliteration":"Waamma man jaaka yasAAa","page":585},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ","translation":"While he fears [Allāh],","transliteration":"Wahuwa yakhsha","page":585},{"numberInSurah":10,"arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","translation":"From him you are distracted.","transliteration":"Faanta AAanhu talahha","page":585},{"numberInSurah":11,"arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌ","translation":"No! Indeed, they [i.e., these verses] are a reminder;","transliteration":"Kalla innaha tathkira","page":585},{"numberInSurah":12,"arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","translation":"So whoever wills may remember it.","transliteration":"Faman shaa thakarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":13,"arabic":"فِى صُحُفٍ مُّكَرَّمَةٍ","translation":"[It is recorded] in honored sheets,","transliteration":"Fee suhufin mukarrama","page":585},{"numberInSurah":14,"arabic":"مَّرْفُوعَةٍ مُّطَهَّرَةٍۭ","translation":"Exalted and purified,","transliteration":"MarfooAAatin mutahhara","page":585},{"numberInSurah":15,"arabic":"بِأَيْدِى سَفَرَةٍ","translation":"[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels,","transliteration":"Bi-aydee safara","page":585},{"numberInSurah":16,"arabic":"كِرَامٍۭ بَرَرَةٍ","translation":"Noble and dutiful.","transliteration":"Kiramin barara","page":585},{"numberInSurah":17,"arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مَآ أَكْفَرَهُۥ","translation":"Destroyed [i.e., cursed] is man; how disbelieving is he.","transliteration":"Qutila al-insanu ma akfarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":18,"arabic":"مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","translation":"From what thing [i.e., substance] did He create him?","transliteration":"Min ayyi shay-in khalaqah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":19,"arabic":"مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","translation":"From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him;","transliteration":"Min nutfatin khalaqahu faqaddarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":20,"arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","translation":"Then He eased the way for him;","transliteration":"Thumma assabeela yassarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":21,"arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقْبَرَهُۥ","translation":"Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him.","transliteration":"Thumma amatahu faaqbarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":22,"arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","translation":"Then when He wills, He will resurrect him.","transliteration":"Thumma itha shaa ansharah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":23,"arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","translation":"No! He [i.e., man] has not yet accomplished what He commanded him.","transliteration":"Kalla lamma yaqdi maamarah","page":585},{"numberInSurah":24,"arabic":"فَلْيَنظُرِ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","translation":"Then let mankind look at his food -","transliteration":"Falyanthuri al-insanuila taAAamih","page":585},{"numberInSurah":25,"arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا ٱلْمَآءَ صَبًّا","translation":"How We poured down water in torrents,","transliteration":"Anna sababna almaasabba","page":585},{"numberInSurah":26,"arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا ٱلْأَرْضَ شَقًّا","translation":"Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts],","transliteration":"Thumma shaqaqna al-arda shaqqa","page":585},{"numberInSurah":27,"arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتْنَا فِيهَا حَبًّا","translation":"And caused to grow within it grain","transliteration":"Faanbatna feeha habba","page":585},{"numberInSurah":28,"arabic":"وَعِنَبًا وَقَضْبًا","translation":"And grapes and herbage","transliteration":"WaAAinaban waqadba","page":585},{"numberInSurah":29,"arabic":"وَزَيْتُونًا وَنَخْلًا","translation":"And olive and palm trees","transliteration":"Wazaytoonan wanakhla","page":585},{"numberInSurah":30,"arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلْبًا","translation":"And gardens of dense shrubbery","transliteration":"Wahada-iqa ghulba","page":585},{"numberInSurah":31,"arabic":"وَفَـٰكِهَةً وَأَبًّا","translation":"And fruit and grass -","transliteration":"Wafakihatan waabba","page":585},{"numberInSurah":32,"arabic":"مَّتَـٰعًا لَّكُمْ وَلِأَنْعَـٰمِكُمْ","translation":"[As] enjoyment [i.e., provision] for you and your grazing livestock.","transliteration":"MataAAan lakum wali-anAAamikum","page":585},{"numberInSurah":33,"arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","translation":"But when there comes the Deafening Blast","transliteration":"Fa-itha jaati assakhkha","page":585},{"numberInSurah":34,"arabic":"يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ","translation":"On the Day a man will flee from his brother","transliteration":"Yawma yafirru almaro min akheeh","page":585},{"numberInSurah":35,"arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","translation":"And his mother and his father","transliteration":"Waommihi waabeeh","page":585},{"numberInSurah":36,"arabic":"وَصَـٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","translation":"And his wife and his children,","transliteration":"Wasahibatihi wabaneeh","page":585},{"numberInSurah":37,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ","translation":"For every man, that Day, will be a matter adequate for him.","transliteration":"Likulli imri-in minhum yawma-ithinsha/nun yughneeh","page":585},{"numberInSurah":38,"arabic":"وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُّسْفِرَةٌ","translation":"[Some] faces, that Day, will be bright -","transliteration":"Wujoohun yawma-ithin musfira","page":585},{"numberInSurah":39,"arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٌ مُّسْتَبْشِرَةٌ","translation":"Laughing, rejoicing at good news.","transliteration":"Dahikatun mustabshira","page":585},{"numberInSurah":40,"arabic":"وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْهَا غَبَرَةٌ","translation":"And [other] faces, that Day, will have upon them dust.","transliteration":"Wawujoohun yawma-ithin AAalayhaghabara","page":585},{"numberInSurah":41,"arabic":"تَرْهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","translation":"Blackness will cover them.","transliteration":"Tarhaquha qatara","page":585},{"numberInSurah":42,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْكَفَرَةُ ٱلْفَجَرَةُ","translation":"Those are the disbelievers, the wicked ones.","transliteration":"Ola-ika humu alkafaratu alfajara","page":585}]}